{"type":null,"faqId":32659,"title":"蓝牙耳机有噪音并且出现断断续续现象怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1.确认是否WLAN开启，若是请关闭WLAN后再看下。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.检查周围是否有无线干扰源，蓝牙距离是否过长，是否有障碍物（例如墙壁）遮挡等。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.将耳机与其它手机连接，是否仍出现同样的问题。若其他手机也出现噪音，请更换其他型号蓝牙耳机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.若使用相同耳机在其他型号/品牌手机无问题，建议您带手机和蓝牙耳机到售后服务网点解决。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7361","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748375000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":12,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"蓝牙耳机,噪音,断断续续","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}